body_html: Had the same problem. One of the steps on the Caffe2 website makes you download the newest versions of third party repos. The newest version of onnx is not compilable though. You can solve the problem by going to the cloned onnx folder, and changing to a working commit. Opening a terminal and writing git checkout 310b44c changed to a commit which I managed to compile.
